          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/936.-step-2-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, peel (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and finely chop (or grate) your<strong> ginger</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) you <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>red</strong> <strong>chilli[es]</strong> in half lengthways, deseed (scrape the seeds out with a teaspoon) and chop finely</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/936.-step-3-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
